########################################
#         The ACCoLiTE project         #
########################################

+-----------------+
|   Description   |
+-----------------+
ACCoLiTE stands for Another C++ COmand-LIne Testing Environment.
It amis to help you writing well-tested C++ projects by doing all the boring stuff about tests.
You just have to focus on writing tests (unfortunatetly, it doesn't do this for you).

